description: The Broan F404211 42 In. White 4-Way Convertible Range Hood is constructed with quality and good looks. The F404211 is superior to the competition whether ducted vertically, horizontally, or non-ducted. The unit is convertible between ducted using a washable aluminum filter (included) and non-ducted (filter purchased separately).The sides are mitered and the bottom edge hemmed, with no sharp edges for safety and good looks. The unit has two-speed fan control and the 2850 RPM motor is permanently lubricated.

The Broan F404211 42 In. White 4-Way Convertible Range Hood is constructed with quality and good looks. The F404211 is superior to the competition whether ducted vertically, horizontally, or non-ducted. The unit is convertible between ducted using a washable aluminum filter (included) and non-ducted (filter purchased separately).The sides are mitered and the bottom edge hemmed, with no sharp edges for safety and good looks. The unit has two-speed fan control and the 2850 RPM motor is permanently lubricated.

  • White 4-way convertible range hood
  • Two speed fan control
  • Polymeric blade and light lens (accepts up to 75W bulb)
  • Washable aluminum filter
  • Converts to non-ducted by removing cover plate from front of hood and installing the non-ducted filter (sold separately)
  • Mitered sides and hemmed bottom for safety and good looks
  • Damper/duct connector included
  • 7-inch round plate included
  • 2850 RPM motor is permanently lubricated
  • 160 CFM and 6.5 Sones with 3.15'' x 10'' (H) or 190 CFM and 6.5 Sones with 7 in. round (V)

short_description:

  • Centrifugal blower, 390 CFM, 6.0 Sones

  • U.L. listed

name: Broan 30'' Hood, 3 speed, aluminum micromesh filter, 4 lamps
description: The Broan QP230BL Evolution 2 30 In. Black Range Hood provides the control, power and lighting you need in four attractive finishes. The sealed flush mount control panel cleans easily, and features simple LED indicators for lighting and blower control. Brilliant lighting from four halogen lamps will satisfy the needs of the most discriminating cooks.
short_description:
The Broan QP230BL Evolution 2 30 In. Black Range Hood provides the control, power and lighting you need in four attractive finishes. The sealed flush mount control panel cleans easily, and features simple LED indicators for lighting and blower control. Brilliant lighting from four halogen lamps will satisfy the needs of the most discriminating cooks.

  • Black Evolution 2 30 inch range hood
  • Non-stick bottom pan for easy cleaning
  • Full filter design with antimicrobial coating inhibits formation of odor-producting bacteria
  • 3-level blower speed control: normal / mid / high
  • Four halogen lamps provide focused lighting for unmatched cooktop visibility
  • 3-level theater-style lighting adjustment
  • Centrifugal blower provides increased performance and quieter operation
  • Advanced Heat Sentry automatically turns blower on to high or higher
  • Design allows for 3-1/4 in. x 10 in., 7 in. round, or non-ducted without repositioning blower
  • CleanSense charcoal filters change color when replacement is necessary

The Allure II provides the style and performance you demand and with DuPont Teflon, the easy clean-up you want. It features very quiet 0.9 Sones at normal speed, powerful 300 CFM high setting, 3-speed electronic control and dishwasher safe micromesh filters. Plus a Standard Heat Sentry detects excessive heat and turns the unit to high speed.

  • White range hood with quiet 0.9 Sones at normal speed 4.5 high
  • 300 CFM high setting
  • 120 volts, 60Hz, 2.0 amps
  • Standard Heat Sentry detects excessive heat and turns unit to high speed
  • 3-speed electronic controls
  • 4-way convertibility
  • DuPont Teflon non-stick bottom cover for easy cleaning
  • Micro-mesh filters, dishwasher safe
  • 3-level light settings; Dual halogen lamp design (bulbs not included)
  • U.L. listed

short_description:
The Broan QS330SS Allure III 30 In. Stainless Steel Under Cabinet Range Hood boasts unparalleled style, quiet, ease of operation and performance. The ultimate Allure model combines modern styling with advanced features like three-speed electronic control plus boost-speed mode, delay-off and filter cleaning reminder. Easy cleaning is assured because for the first time anywhere, you can have the easy cleaning of DuPont Teflon in a range hood.

  • Stainless steel 30 in. range hood
  • Ultra quiet 0.4 Sones and 300 CFM at normal speed; in Boost mode 430 CFM and 8.0 Sones
  • Easy to clean DuPont Teflopn bottom pan with fully enclosed design
  • Professional style dishwasher safe filters
  • Three-level light settings; dual halogen lamp design (bulbs not included)
  • Advanced Heat Sentry detects excessive heat and adjusts hood speed for proper ventilation
  • Centrifugal blower provides increased performance and quieter operation
  • Adjustable duct connectors - accommodate off-center duct-work
  • CleanSense charcoal filters change colors when replacement is necessary
  • U.L. listed
